<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Why are the nations in turmoil,</para>

<para style="q1">and why do the peoples make plots that will fail?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />The kings of the earth take their stand together</para>

<para style="q1">and the rulers conspire together</para>

<para style="q1">against Yahweh and against his Messiah, saying,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />"Let us tear off the shackles they put on us</para>

<para style="q1">and throw off their chains."</para>
